  <brief_title>Treatment of Incomplete Abortion With 600 Mcg Oral Misoprostol Compared to Standard Surgical Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Misoprostol for Treatment of Incomplete Abortion</official_title>
  <sponsors>
