  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to compare the efficacy, side effects profile and acceptability of a single
      dose of 600mcg misoprostol taken orally compared to standard surgical treatment as per local
      protocols for the treatment of incomplete abortion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
